infographic relation-dagre-flow-tb-badge-card
data
  title Symphony, Codex, skills, and ops
  desc Operations automation may decide and orchestrate, but mutation still lives in ranctl.
  nodes
    - id incident
      label Incident or request
      desc External trigger
    - id workflow
      label Symphony workflow
      desc Workflow coordination
    - id codex
      label Codex reasoning
      desc Decision support
    - id skill
      label Skill selection
      desc Procedure wrapper choice
    - id ranctl
      label bin/ranctl <command>
      desc Deterministic execution
    - id lifecycle
      label Plan / approval / apply / verify / rollback
      desc Mutable runtime path
    - id evidence
      label Artifacts / observability
      desc Telemetry and evidence path
  relations
    incident -> workflow
    workflow -> codex
    codex -> skill
    skill -> ranctl
    ranctl -> lifecycle
    ranctl -> evidence
theme
  palette #0f766e #1d4ed8 #0f172a #ea580c #475569 #7c3aed
  base
    text
      font-family Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif
